  "privacyPolicyAppTitle": "GO FULL — Privacy Policy",
  "privacyPolicyLastUpdate": "Last updated: April 2026",
  "privacyPolicyFooter": "© 2026 GO FULL. All rights reserved.",
  "privacyIntroTitle": "Introduction",
  "privacyIntroBody": "Welcome to the GO FULL Drivers app. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when using our services as a driver or service provider.",
  "privacyDataTitle": "Data We Collect",
  "privacyDataBody": "• Name, phone number, and registration data\n• ID and driving license photos\n• Your location during service delivery\n• Order details and financial transactions\n• Vehicle data and insurance information\n• Device information to improve performance",
  "privacyUsageTitle": "How We Use Your Data",
  "privacyUsageBody": "• Operating fuel supply and vehicle towing services\n• Locating you to route nearby orders\n• Calculating earnings and processing payments\n• Evaluating service quality and your performance\n• Communicating with you about orders and updates\n• Ensuring transaction safety and security",
  "privacySharingTitle": "Data Sharing",
  "privacySharingBody": "• We share your name, phone number, and vehicle info with the customer during an order\n• We share your current location with the customer to track your arrival\n• We do not sell your personal data to any third parties\n• We may share anonymized data for analytical purposes",
  "privacyProtectionTitle": "Data Protection",
  "privacyProtectionBody": "We use advanced encryption technologies to protect your data. We retain your data only as long as your account is active or as required by law. All information is stored on secure servers with continuous monitoring.",
  "privacyLocationTitle": "Location Data",
  "privacyLocationBody": "We use your geographic location only while your status is set to \"Available\" or during order execution. You can stop sharing your location at any time by changing your status to \"Unavailable\". Your location is not tracked outside working hours.",
  "privacyRightsTitle": "Your Rights",
  "privacyRightsBody": "• Request access to your personal data\n• Request correction or update of your data\n• Request deletion of your account and data\n• Withdraw your consent at any time\n• File a complaint with relevant authorities",
  "privacyContactTitle": "Contact Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions about the privacy policy or how your data is handled, please contact us through the in-app support section or email us at: support@gofull.ly",
