  "privacyCopyright": "© 2026 GO FULL. All rights reserved.",
  "privacyDriverIntroBody": "Welcome to the GO FULL driver app. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This policy explains how we collect, use and protect your information when using our services as a driver or service provider.",
  "privacyDriverDataCollectedTitle": "Data We Collect",
  "privacyDriverDataCollectedBody": "• Name, phone number, and registration data\n• ID photos and driving license\n• Your geographic location during service delivery\n• Order details and financial transactions\n• Vehicle data and insurance information\n• Device information to improve performance",
  "privacyDriverDataUseTitle": "How We Use Your Data",
  "privacyDriverDataUseBody": "• Operating fuel delivery and vehicle towing services\n• Determining your location to route nearby orders to you\n• Calculating earnings and processing payments\n• Evaluating service quality and your performance\n• Communicating with you about orders and updates\n• Ensuring transaction security and safety",
  "privacyDriverDataShareTitle": "Data Sharing",
  "privacyDriverDataShareBody": "• We share your name, phone number and vehicle information with the customer during orders\n• We share your current location with the customer to track your arrival\n• We do not sell your personal data to any third parties\n• We may share anonymized data for analytical purposes",
  "privacyDriverDataProtectionTitle": "Data Protection",
  "privacyDriverDataProtectionBody": "We use advanced encryption technologies to protect your data. We retain your data only as long as your account is active or as required by law. All information is stored on secure servers with continuous monitoring.",
  "privacyDriverLocationTitle": "Location Data",
  "privacyDriverLocationBody": "We use your geographic location only when your status is set to 'Available' or during order execution. You can stop sharing your location at any time by changing your status to 'Unavailable'. Your location is not tracked outside working hours.",
  "privacyDriverRightsTitle": "Your Rights",
  "privacyDriverRightsBody": "• Request access to your personal data\n• Request correction or update of your data\n• Request deletion of your account and data\n• Withdraw your consent at any time\n• File a complaint with the relevant authorities",
  "privacyDriverContactTitle": "Contact Us",
  "privacyDriverContactBody": "If you have any questions about the privacy policy or how your data is handled, please contact us through the technical support section in the app or email us at: support@gofull.ly",
  "fuelDetailsSection": "Fuel Details"
